Package org.ndeftools.externaltype

Interface Summary
ExternalTypeRecord.ExternalTypeRecordParser Interface which simplifies adding your own External Type records.
 

Class Summary
AndroidApplicationRecord Android Application Record.
ExternalTypeRecord External type record.

Note: Support for custom external types can be added via the ExternalTypeRecord.ExternalTypeRecordParser interface, or by overloading this class.
GenericExternalTypeRecord Generic ExternalTypeRecord for any domain, type and data.
